<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Services - Greymatter Accountancy</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Sora:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header', { rootPath: '../', currentPage: 'page' }) %>

  <section class="page-header page-header-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Our Core Services</h1>
      <p>Complete financial solutions tailored to your needs</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services services-page">
    <div class="container">
      
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-magnifying-glass"></i></div>
          <h3>Audit & Assurance</h3>
          <p>Independent, UK-compliant audits that build stakeholder confidence. We follow FRS 102/105 and ISA (UK) standards. Perfect for companies requiring statutory audits or lender assurance.</p>
          <a href="../index.html#contact" class="service-link">Discuss this service <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i></div>
          <h3>Tax Reporting</h3>
          <p>Full UK tax compliance — Corporation Tax, Self Assessment, VAT, and ERS. We file directly to HMRC and help you plan, not just comply.</p>
          <a href="../index.html#contact" class="service-link">Discuss this service <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-book"></i></div>
          <h3>Bookkeeping</h3>
          <p>Daily, weekly, or monthly transaction management via Xero, QuickBooks, or FreeAgent. Clean books = real-time decisions.</p>
          <a href="../index.html#contact" class="service-link">Discuss this service <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i></div>
          <h3>Management Accounts</h3>
          <p>Not just for year-end. Get P&L, balance sheets, and KPIs every month to steer your London business with confidence.</p>
          <a href="../index.html#contact" class="service-link">Discuss this service <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i></div>
          <h3>VAT & Making Tax Digital</h3>
          <p>Making Tax Digital ready. VAT returns, partial exemption, and scheme advice (flat rate, cash accounting, annual).</p>
          <a href="../index.html#contact" class="service-link">Discuss this service <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i></div>
          <h3>Company Secretarial</h3>
          <p>Confirmation statements, share filings, and Companies House compliance — handled proactively.</p>
          <a href="../index.html#contact" class="service-link">Discuss this service <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Need Help Choosing the Right Services?</h2>
      <p>Let's discuss your requirements in a free consultation.</p>
      <a href="../index.html#contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </section>
  <%- include('partials/footer', { rootPath: '../', currentPage: 'page' }) %>
</body>
</html>
